<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Join a Team - FTC Starter Hub</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/main.css?v=13">
</head>
<body>
  <header></header>
  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Join an FTC Team</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Learn how to find and join an existing FIRST Tech Challenge robotics team.</p>

      <p>
        <a href="/join-form" class="btn btn-primary">Sign Up to Join a Team →</a>
      </p>

      <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary back-button">← Back Home</a>
      
      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>Why Join an FTC Team?</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Learn Real Engineering:</strong> Design, build, and program actual robots</li>
          <li><strong>Teamwork Skills:</strong> Collaborate with peers toward a common goal</li>
          <li><strong>Problem-Solving:</strong> Face real engineering challenges</li>
          <li><strong>Competition Experience:</strong> Test your skills against other teams</li>
          <li><strong>College Opportunities:</strong> Great for college applications and scholarships</li>
          <li><strong>Networking:</strong> Connect with mentors and like-minded students</li>
          <li><strong>Fun &amp; Excitement:</strong> Build amazing robots and compete!</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      
      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>Step 1: Find Teams in Your Area</h2>
        <div class="content-subsection">
          <h3>Official FIRST Website</h3>
          <p>Visit <strong>firstinspires.org</strong> and use their team finder.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>Key Takeaways</h2>
        <div class="example-box">
          <ul>
            <li>Use FIRST's website to find teams near you</li>
            <li>Attend meetings to see if the team is right for you</li>
            <li>No prior experience needed - teams welcome beginners</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
  <script src="/assets/js/main.js?v=8"></script>
</body>
</html>
